 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
           LegSem LegStar Common Eclipse plugin Version 1.0.1
                           Release Notes
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PREREQUISITES:

 This plugin requires Eclipse 3.2.1.
 
INSTALLING/UNINSTALLING:

  [[1]] Within Eclipse, create a remote site using:
 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Help-->Software Updates-->Find and Install-->Search for new features-->New Remote site
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  
  Have the URL point to http://www.legsem.com/legstar/eclipse/update and select the
    Common feature.

 [[2]] Restart Eclipse and check that "Legstar Commons" shows up in:
 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Help-->About Eclipse SDK-->Plug-in details
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   
 [[3]] To uninstall, use:

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Help-->Software Updates-->Manage Configurations.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  then right-click on the feature you wish to uninstall.

DOCUMENTATION:

 Documentation available at http://www.legsem.com/legstar/common-plugin

